OL,6,FMore than 100 maternity cases at
OL,7,Fscandal-hit Nottingham University
OL,8,FHospitals (NUH) Trust are being
OL,9,Freviewed by police.
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Police announced a
OL,12,Fcriminal investigation in September
OL,13,Flast year into concerns raised about
OL,14,Fsevere harm allegedly linked to
OL,15,Fmaternity services at the Trust.
OL,17,FThe force said the number of referrals
OL,18,Fis expected to increase while it
OL,19,Freceives information from the largest
OL,20,Fever NHS maternity review led by
OL,21,Fformer senior midwife Donna Ockenden.
