OL,6,FMs Ockenden's review now includes
OL,7,Fnearly 2,000 experiences of maternity
OL,8,Fcare at NUH, including deaths and
OL,9,Finjuries, and a police spokesman said
OL,10,Fthat they are asking her review team
OL,11,Fto provide information on all cases
OL,12,Fheld.
OL,14,FOver two years since she launched her
OL,15,Freview into maternity care at
OL,16,FNottingham's hospitals, Ms Ockenden
OL,17,Fsaid she is still concerned over the
OL,18,Fcare some women are receiving.
