OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Rob Griffin
OL,7,Fsaid: "Affected families remain at the
OL,8,Fheart of our investigation into
OL,9,Fmaternity care provision at Nottingham
OL,10,FUniversity Hospitals.
OL,12,F"We are receiving information from
OL,13,FDonna Ockenden's review team and our
OL,14,Fapproach is being underpinned by
OL,15,Fcompassion, care and candour toward
OL,16,Fthose affected.
