OL,6,F"Currently more than 100 cases have
OL,7,Fbeen referred to us. I expect the
OL,8,Fnumber of referrals will further
OL,9,Fincrease and all cases will be
OL,10,Fmeticulously investigated by a team of
OL,11,Fskilled and professional investigators
OL,12,Fwho are dedicated to this case."
OL,14,FTracy Pilcher, chief nurse at NUH,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We welcome Donna's feedback and
OL,16,Fthe opportunities it provides us to
OL,17,Fcontinue to improve our maternity
OL,18,Fservices.
